New prospects for the management of cardiovascular effects of tyrosine kinase 
inhibitors in patients with chronic myeloid leukemia.

[Article in English, Portuguese]

Almeida AG(1), Almeida A(2), Melo T(3), Guerra L(4), Lopes L(5), Ribeiro P(6), 
Duarte M(7), Mota A(8), Fontes-Carvalho R(9).

Author information:
(1)Serviço de Cardiologia, Hospital Universitário de Santa Maria (CHLN), Centro 
