Design of a typical residence for the elderly in Morocco.

Bouaoudate M(1), Harti JE(1), Maamar M(2), Abouqal R(3).

Author information:
(1)Laboratory of Medicinal Chemistry and Hospital Pharmacy, Faculty of Medicine 
